{"tid":2291751,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"陳雲講d野真定假？？","createTime":"2020-11-19T04:10:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-19T11:39:40.000Z","uid":228143,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4948a359213ed3124aaab7d3cc0023119a598e70","tid":2291751,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T04:10:34.000Z","msg":"陳雲：政府準備將旅館納入防疫法例的表列場所，是侵犯私人租用的地方，而那個地方是用作個人起居的寢室。這情況，如同授權政府隨時闖入你的睡房，搜查你衣櫃有無躲藏人物，觀看你赤裸的身體！這是文革期間的大陸旅館的情況，半夜公安持槍拍門入內檢查。<br />\n<br />\n很多人沒理會到這種表列的伸延，它之後可以伸延到你的住宅！<br />\n公式是這樣的，大家見慣了：首先是找人貼出Staycation的離譜例子，之後KOL帶頭嘲笑好離譜，而網民不知道這是侵犯一個公民租用的私人居所，跟住一齊起哄嘲笑。之後，政府立法管制！<br />\n<br />\n租用旅館、與租用一個service apartment，與租用一個屋宇管理公司的住宅，只是租用的日子有別，法例好容易延伸過去。 <br />\n這種法例，怎可以給它通過？<br />\n<br />\n全香港，只剩下陳雲在呼喚香港人關注人權和人身自由，議員、律師、人權組織都彷彿被滅聲了。可憐嗎？陳雲只是一個文人，可憐他連人權律師都要做埋！"},{"pid":"e04a666b7b6050b5aeee037deaabffee5c04e1f7","tid":2291751,"uid":51701,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T04:29:39.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><p class=\"center\">扮燒山fans嘅雲糞<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O0vOfJ0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO0vOfJ0.jpg&h=d9a57d1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PGVnkaG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPGVnkaG.jpg&h=22e80bf0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8K3j6QH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8K3j6QH.jpg&h=bc059408&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bsF24Co.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbsF24Co.jpg&h=1fa7a04c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ec3Rf7Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEc3Rf7Z.jpg&h=32b72de7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PjOawGh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi